   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"12" height=3D"24" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$R$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4503px;vertical-=
align:-5px"></span>
   are strictly positive.
</p>
</div></div>
<p>
   Note that
