<h2 id=3D"hid4" class=3D"subsection">Uniqueness of the decomposition</h2>
<p>
   The QR decomposition is unique.
</p>
<div class=3D"proposition">
   <p><span class=3D"titoletto">Proposition</span>
      Under the assumptions of the previous proposition, the QR decompositi=
on is
      unique, that is, the matrices
      <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"14" height=3D"25" src=
=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAA=
AICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$Q$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4406px;verti=
cal-align:-5px"></span>
      and
      <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"12" height=3D"24" src=
=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAA=
AICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$R$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4503px;verti=
cal-align:-5px"></span>
      satisfying the stated properties are unique.
   </p>
</div>

<div class=3D"bproof"><span class=3D"bproof">Proof</span></div>
<div id=3D"idn2" class=3D"clps"><div class=3D"proofline">
