EAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq33]" style=3D"background-position:0px -2893px=
;"></span>where
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"21" height=3D"24" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$PS$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4340px;vertical=
-align:-5px"></span>
