   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"11" height=3D"24" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$S$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4552px;vertical-=
align:-5px"></span>
   having strictly positive diagonal elements. Since the columns of
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"14" height=3D"25" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$Q$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4406px;vertical-=
align:-5px"></span>
