   that<span class=3D"displayed"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"73" height=3D"3=
8" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAA=
BAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq50]" style=3D"background-position:0px -336=
4px;"></span>where
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"22" height=3D"25" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$Q^{=07st }$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4270px;=
vertical-align:-5px"></span>
   is the  <a href=3D"https://www.statlect.com/matrix-algebra/conjugate-tra=
nspose">conjugate transpose</a>
   of
   <span class=3D"inm"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"14" height=3D"25" src=3D"=
data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$Q$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4406px;vertical-=
align:-5px"></span>.
   As a
   consequence,<span class=3D"displayed"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"136" he=
ight=3D"38" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAA=
AALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq51]" style=3D"background-position=
:0px -2495px;"></span>
</p>
<p>
   If
