data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICR=
AEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"$Q$" style=3D"background-position:0px -4406px;vertical-=
align:-5px"></span>
   has only real entries, then the conjugate transpose coincides with the
   transpose and the two equations above
   become<span class=3D"displayed"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"72" height=3D=
"38" src=3D"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAANvf7wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAA=
AABAAEAAAICRAEAOw=3D=3D" alt=3D"[eq52]" style=3D"background-position:0px -3=
402px;"></span>and<span class=3D"displayed"><img class=3D"sp" width=3D"75" =
